<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Billboard</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@v2.15.1/devicon.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/themes.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body class="<%= user.preferences.theme === 'dark' ? 'dark-theme' : '' %>">

    <%- include('partials/header', { user: user }) %>

    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>An elegant space for your ideas.</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Billboard is more than just a note-taking app; it's a clean, organized, and beautiful environment designed to help you focus.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="about-main-content">
        <div class="container">

            <section class="about-feature-section">
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h2>Inspired by Simplicity</h2>
                    <p>The original idea was to recreate the satisfying feeling of a physical corkboard. A simple place to pin thoughts, organize them visually with drag-and-drop, and customize the look and feel to make the space truly your own.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-image">
                    <img src="/img/billboard-screenshot.png" alt="Billboard App Screenshot">
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="tech-stack-showcase">
                <h2>Built With Modern & Robust Technologies</h2>
                <div class="tech-stack-list">
                    <div class="tech-item" title="Node.js"><i class="devicon-nodejs-plain-wordmark"></i></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="Express.js"><i class="devicon-express-original-wordmark"></i></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="MongoDB"><i class="devicon-mongodb-plain-wordmark"></i></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="JavaScript"><i class="devicon-javascript-plain"></i></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="EJS"><span class="tech-text">EJS</span></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="CSS3"><i class="devicon-css3-plain-wordmark"></i></div>
                    <div class="tech-item" title="HTML5"><i class="devicon-html5-plain-wordmark"></i></div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-feature-section reverse">
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h2>About the Creator</h2>
                    <p>My name is Pierre, a passionate web developer from Trois-Rivi√®res, QC. I enjoy building useful and beautiful applications from scratch. This project is a demonstration of my skills in back-end logic, database management, and creating interactive user interfaces.</p>
                    <div class="social-links-about">
                        <a href="https://github.com/Rolens1" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub</a>
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pierre-cheridor-38754a1b2/" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-image">
                    <img src="/img/pierre-photo.jpg" alt="Pierre Cheridor">
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/javascript/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>